PrecisOrder which provides for (a) the transfer of ownership to the NEWFOUNDLAND LIGHT AND POWER COMPANY LIMITED with respect to the material electricity distribution system located in the Pleasantville district of the City of St. John's, Newfoundland; and (b) the granting of a Licence which will permit them to occupy and use the grounds associated with these works for a term of twenty (20) years.
